<h3>Intersectional feminism = dalit woman</h3>
<h4>Dalit&nbsp;<em>women</em>&nbsp;confront a “triple burden” in our country as they face caste discrimination, gender bias, and economic deprivation.&nbsp;</h4>
<p>Reservation in parliament = 33% (108 caa bill) , horizontal for dalit women?&nbsp;</p>
<h3>Caste in daily life</h3>
<p>not letting the house helpers eat or drink in the same utensils that we use</p>
<p>telling them to sit on the ﬂoors while the rest of us sit on chairs,</p>
<p>not letting them step into the kitchen or cook food due to their caste,</p>